\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I resolved to be done with it. It was then that I realized that there is only. I\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92ve chosen to delve into the mysteries of the Black.\u8221\'94}
