\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, please. Don\u8217\'92t act like you didn\u8217\'92t already know the answer. You\u8217\'92ve thought of it, too. Only, you\u8217\'92re too much of a . You absolve your conscious by deferring the indignity to me. Which, I hope you know, makes you worse than me. Not only will their death be on your hands, but so will the stain of shirking responsibility. Well, I won\u8217\'92t let you off so easy. When the gods are all dead, you\u8217\'92ll have no one left to repent to but to yourself, and to }{\f2\fs24\b0\i1\cf1 me}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 . I will not forgive you for it.\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8221\'94}
