\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 She sped towards the horizon. There, a }{\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 wide, rolling cloud of smoke billowed out a line of fire. The battle there had been raging for days. Hundreds of thousands had already perished. Such was the glut of death that the magic\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92d smoke feeding on it had grown into a god in its own right, deserving of a name. Its stomach flashed with }{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 lightning, and all her thoughts were subsumed by the rolling drum of sequent thunder.}
\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
